        "description": "在130°C下，使用80% Hf1.5TPA/MCM-41催化剂催化环戊酮和环己酮的羟醛缩合反应4小时。",
        "text_snippet": "The aldol condensation of cyclopentanone and cyclohexanone was conducted in a 25 mL three-necked round-bottom flask. Typically, 2.00 g cyclopentanone, 2.33 g cyclohexanone and 0.43 g catalyst were added into the flask, and the reaction was conducted at 130 °C for 4 h.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Aldol condensation reaction"
      },
      {
        "experiment_id": 2,
        "reaction_type": "羟醛缩合反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Aldol condensation reaction",
        "description": "使用80% Hf1.5TPA/MCM-41催化剂，通过温度梯度法（150°C反应10小时后降温至100°C再反应6小时）催化木质纤维素酮混合物（包含环庚酮、丁醛、环戊酮和环己酮）的共羟醛缩合反应。",
        "text_snippet": "The co-aldol condensation of lignocellulosic ketones mixture was conducted in a 25 mL three-necked round-bottom flask. 0.34 g 80 %Hf1.5TPA/MCM-41 and 3.40 g lignocellulosic ketones... Firstly, cycloheptanone, butyraldehyde, cyclopentanone (half amount) and cyclohexanone (half amount) were added into the reactor with catalyst for reaction at 150 °C. After 10 h, the temperature was reduced to 100 °C and the remaining feedstock was added to react for 6 h.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Aldol condensation reaction"
      }
    ]
  },
